  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to characterise the influence of the autonomic nervous system activity on the
      development of the lipodystrophy syndrome in HIV-infected patients by measuring heart rate
      variability and various metabolic pathways in HIV patients receiving highly active
      antiretroviral therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
